# Next.js App Router Component Generator

When asked to generate a Next.js component, follow the instructions in:
`.claude/skills/component-gen-next/SKILL.md`

## Quick Reference

**Usage:** Specify component name + description. Framework is always Next.js App Router.
- RSC by default (no directive)
- `'use client'` only for interactive islands

**Required (`--type feature`):** Suspense skeleton + error boundary + empty check + async await.

**BANNED:**
- `: any` in TypeScript
- `useQuery` in Server Components (use `await`)
- `next/router` (use `next/navigation`)
- `export const revalidate` (use `'use cache'`)

For full protocol: read `.claude/skills/component-gen-next/SKILL.md`
